{
  "texts": [
    "It's not easy to decide the correctness of the comments automatically.",
    "Therefore, we manually calculate CR to ensure its trustworthiness during the evaluation.",
    "The higher CR is, the better DeGPT behaves in appending comments.",
    "• Non-trivial Rate of Comments (NR): Considering only the correctness of comments is not enough, we also need to consider whether the comments added by DeGPT can help understand the program.",
    "We define a comment as trivial if it merely states the behavior of the program statement."
  ]
}